is at hand!

880
01:06:27,500 --> 01:06:28,750
Brother.

881
01:06:39,708 --> 01:06:41,833
<i>Put down your weapon.</i>

882
01:06:41,875 --> 01:06:43,125
<i>Remember what
I taught you.</i>

883
01:06:43,167 --> 01:06:46,000
He who lives by the sword
will die by the sword.

884
01:06:46,042 --> 01:06:48,583
<i>Put down your weapon.</i>

885
01:07:11,000 --> 01:07:13,500
Who is it
that you seek?

886
01:07:13,542 --> 01:07:16,417
Jesus of Nazareth.

887
01:07:23,625 --> 01:07:25,875
I am he.

888
01:07:49,000 --> 01:07:50,833
Lord!

889
01:08:04,375 --> 01:08:06,875
<i>This is a
tale for the ages.</i>

890
01:08:06,917 --> 01:08:09,333
<i>You swear it all
happened as you say?</i>

891
01:08:09,375 --> 01:08:11,917
Every word.

892
01:08:11,958 --> 01:08:14,708
So they took
Lord Jesus-

893
01:08:14,792 --> 01:08:16,125
<i>your Lord Jesus-</i>

894
01:08:16,167 --> 01:08:17,833
and they crucified him?

895
01:08:17,875 --> 01:08:20,458
<i>Tell me of that.</i>

896
01:08:20,500 --> 01:08:23,333
it was-

897
