01:14:08,667 --> 01:14:11,708
Do you love me?

997
01:14:11,750 --> 01:14:15,583
You know I do
with all my heart.

998
01:14:15,625 --> 01:14:20,208
Then you must choose,
for my path is with Christ.

999
01:14:20,250 --> 01:14:23,292
Where does
your path lead?

1000
01:14:23,375 --> 01:14:24,583
I don't know.

1001
01:14:24,667 --> 01:14:27,875
You have taken counsel
with Simon Peter himself.

1002
01:14:27,917 --> 01:14:31,333
You have heard
the truth from his lips.

1003
01:14:31,375 --> 01:14:36,625
What more do you
need to hear?

1004
01:14:38,875 --> 01:14:41,375
Nothing.

1005
01:14:41,417 --> 01:14:46,292
I need nothing more.

1006
01:14:46,333 --> 01:14:50,792
Do you still
seek his blessing?

1007
01:14:50,875 --> 01:14:52,750
Wait here.

1008
01:15:01,458 --> 01:15:04,917
<i>Time's up, Ô¨Åsherman.</i>

1009
01:15:05,000 --> 01:15:07,625
<i>Third day breaks.</i>

1010
01:15:07,708 --> 01:15:11,958
<i>You are mine.</i>

1011
01:15:12,042 --> 01:15:14,833
I fear no evil.

1012
01:15:14,917 --> 01:15:17,958
Christ has victory
over you.

1013
01:15:20,250 --> 01:15:26,958
My fate is
sealed by Christ.

1014
01:15:38,333 --> 01:15:42,042
I just have one
last question.

1015
01:15:42,083 --> 01:15:45,625
<i>Where did you find the strength
to become the man that you are,</i>

1016
01:15:45,708 --> 01:15:49,333
from an ordinary fisherman
to a great apostle?

1017
01:15:49,375 --> 01:15:53,458
<i>People line up just so that
your shadow might fall on them.</i>

1018
01:15:53,500 --> 01:15:55,625
<i>What caused
this transformation?</i>

1019
01:15:55,708 --> 01:15:59,708
It was all God.

1020
01:15:59,750 --> 01:16:02,542
<i>Jesus chose me.</i>

1021
01:16:02,583 --> 01:16:06,208
He walked with me
and taught me.

1022
01:16:06,250 --> 01:16:12,042
He gave me the
Holy Spirit to guide me,

1023
01:16:12,083 --> 01:16:16,875
<i>and God has a plan
for you, too.</i>

1024
01:16:21,708 --> 01:16:24,292
The wager is yours,
Simon Peter.

1025
01:16:24,375 --> 01:16:26,083
<i>You have won.</i>

1026
01:16:26,167 --> 01:16:28,000
<i>I have decided.</i>

1027
01:16:28,042 --> 01:16:31,208
I will stand with you
and as Christ is my Lord.

1028
01:16:31,250 --> 01:16:32,875
Now come, I will
take you out of here

1029
01:16:32,958 --> 01:16:35,833
before the shift changes.

1030
01:16:35,917 --> 01:16:39,708
Jesus Christ
welcomes you

1031
01:16:39,708 --> 01:16:44,125
with honor and love,
Martinian,

1032
01:16:44,167 --> 01:16:46,667
but I cannot
go with you.

1033
01:16:46,708 --> 01:16:49,083
<i>That would only
endanger you.</i>

1034
01:16:49,125 --> 01:16:50,500
I will die.

1035
01:16:50,583 --> 01:16:51,792
Oh, cursed on that.

1036
01:16:51,875 --> 01:16:54,083
I thought you
would say that.

1037
01:16:54,125 --> 01:16:55,583
Hold on.

1038
01:17:13,750 --> 01:17:15,000
What have you done?

1039
01:17:15,042 --> 01:17:16,250
You would not
come to her.

1040
01:17:16,292 --> 01:17:18,125
What else
was I to do?

1041
01:17:18,208 --> 01:17:20,583
This is dangerous.

1042
01:17:20,625 --> 01:17:23,792
<i>Simon Peter,
apostle of Christ,</i>

1043
01:17:23,833 --> 01:17:28,625
I beg you,
give me your blessing.

1044
01:17:30,833 --> 01:17:35,708
<i>Novella, is your
life given over to Jesus?</i>

1045
01:17:35,708 --> 01:17:40,583
<i>Do you claim him to be
your Lord and salvation?</i>

1046
01:17:40,625 --> 01:17:42,542
<i>Yes.</i>

1047
01:17:42,583 --> 01:17:47,042
Then you shall
be blessed as you desire.

1048
01:17:47,083 --> 01:17:51,333
<i>Accept this blessing in the
glorious name of the Father,</i>

1049
01:17:51,417 --> 01:17:54,167
His Son Jesus Christ,

1050
01:17:54,208 --> 01:17:55,458
and the Holy-

1051
01:17:56,417 --> 01:17:59,292
<i>Processus.</i>

1052
01:18:00,125 --> 01:18:01,500
<i>Processus,
what are you doing?</i>

1053
01:18:01,542 --> 01:18:02,750
Do you like
persecution so much

1054
01:18:02,875 --> 01:18:04,333
that you want
to partake of it?

1055
01:18:04,375 --> 01:18:06,250
You heard his words,
as well as I.

1056
01:18:06,292 --> 01:18:10,250
Did you not hear
the truth in them?

1057
01:18:10,333 --> 01:18:12,750
They were just stories.

1058
01:18:12,792 --> 01:18:15,375
What of Christ,
the man himself?

1059
01:18:15,458 --> 01:18:17,875
His words, his followers are
spreading across the land,

1060
01:18:17,917 --> 01:18:19,625
fulfilling prophecies,
performing miracles,

1061
01:18:19,667 --> 01:18:21,750
risen from the dead,
that is no story!

1062
01:18:21,833 --> 01:18:23,500
He was a rebel,
and his followers are outlaws!

1063
01:18:23,583 --> 01:18:25,083
That is what
the emperor says.

1064
01:18:25,125 --> 01:18:26,750
What do you think?

1065
01:18:26,833 --> 01:18:29,667
Am I an outlaw?
My wife?

1066
01:18:29,708 --> 01:18:31,000
Would you see us
tortured and killed?

1067
01:18:31,042 --> 01:18:32,583
<i>You're asking
me to disobey my command!</i>

1068
01:18:32,667 --> 01:18:34,750
I'm asking you
to think for your soul,

1069
01:18:34,792 --> 01:18:36,208
the part of you that
will live forever.

1070
01:18:36,292 --> 01:18:37,500
Stop confusing me!

1071
01:18:37,583 --> 01:18:39,583
Let go of your anger,
your distrust.

1072
01:18:39,625 --> 01:18:42,000
How dare you
talk down to me.

1073
01:18:42,042 --> 01:18:43,292
I am arresting you!

1074
01:18:43,333 --> 01:18:44,833
Let him into
your heart.

1075
01:18:44,917 --> 01:18:46,125
Shut your mouth!

1076
01:18:46,167 --> 01:18:47,417
Save yourself!

1077
01:18:47,458 --> 01:18:48,708
I said shut up!

1078
01:18:49,000 --> 01:18:50,250
Martinian!

1079
01:18:55,333 --> 01:18:56,625
Strike me
all you want.

1080
01:18:56,667 --> 01:18:58,167
I am your friend
and I love you.

1081
01:18:58,208 --> 01:19:00,208
Christ our Lord
loves you.

1082
01:19:20,792 --> 01:19:24,375
Come Process us.

1083
01:19:24,458 --> 01:19:30,792
Receive Jesus as your Savior
and be free of all your sins.

1084
01:19:54,708 --> 01:20:01,250
God the Father,
you have given us salvation.

1085
01:20:01,292 --> 01:20:06,083
Touch these hearts,
as today they recognize

1086
01:20:06,167 --> 01:20:09,167
their need for you,

1087
01:20:09,250 --> 01:20:13,458
<i>and they wish to accept
Jesus as Lord.</i>

1088
01:20:13,500 --> 01:20:15,250
Processus,

1089
01:20:15,333 --> 01:20:17,667
<i>Martinfan,</i>

1090
01:20:17,750 --> 01:20:21,375
<i>pray with me.</i>

1091
01:20:21,417 --> 01:20:25,208
<i>"Lord, I accept
Jesus as my Savior,</i>

1092
01:20:25,292 --> 01:20:31,167
<i>and I thank you
for the forgiveness of sin. "</i>

1093
01:20:31,208 --> 01:20:35,958
<i>Lord,
I accept Jesus as my Savior,</i>

1094
01:20:36,042 --> 01:20:39,458
<i>and I thank you
for the forgiveness of sin.</i>

1095
01:20:40,500 --> 01:20:43,000
<i>Amen.</i>

1096
01:20:43,083 --> 01:20:44,500
Amen.

1097
01:20:47,667 --> 01:20:49,583
Amen.

1098
01:20:50,708 --> 01:20:55,500
Novella, you seek
the blessing of Christ.

1099
01:21:01,083 --> 01:21:02,625
May I ask?

1100
01:21:02,667 --> 01:21:06,917
We are without child.

1101
01:21:07,000 --> 01:21:12,500
"I will withhold no good
thing from those who love me,

1102
01:21:12,542 --> 01:21:16,500
says the Lord.

1103
01:21:16,542 --> 01:21:19,083
Go in peace.

1104
01:21:19,167 --> 01:21:21,375
<i>Thank you.</i>

1105
01:21:37,833 --> 01:21:39,458
<i>How many times
have I told the guards?</i>

1106
01:21:39,542 --> 01:21:43,000
<i>Political prisoners on the left,
religious fanatics on the right.</i>

1107
01:21:43,083 --> 01:21:46,042
Do I have to do everything
myself around here?

1108
01:21:46,125 --> 01:21:49,167
You two,
where's your prisoner?

1109
01:21:49,208 --> 01:21:52,000
It is past dawn,
you great louts.

1110
01:21:52,042 --> 01:21:53,583
He is to be crucified.

1111
01:21:53,625 --> 01:21:54,875
Bind him and take him.

1112
01:21:54,917 --> 01:21:57,250
We need the cell for another.
Who is it?

1113
01:21:57,292 --> 01:22:00,667
Sir, another
Christian, Saul of Tarsus.

1114
01:22:00,708 --> 01:22:01,917
They're crawling
out of the walls,

1115
01:22:01,958 --> 01:22:05,458
these Christians!

1116
01:22:16,625 --> 01:22:20,708
This is gonna be the hardest
thing I've ever done.

1117
01:22:40,500 --> 01:22:42,875
Is it time?

1118
01:22:42,917 --> 01:22:44,750
It's time,
Simon Peter.

1119
01:22:44,792 --> 01:22:47,542
The cell is required
for another Christian prisoner,

1120
01:22:47,583 --> 01:22:50,750
a certain
Saul of Tars us.

1121
01:22:50,792 --> 01:22:54,542
Paul, my old friend.

1122
01:22:58,250 --> 01:23:00,500
Teacher,
I cannot do this.

1123
01:23:00,583 --> 01:23:01,792
I cannot do this.

1124
01:23:01,875 --> 01:23:04,083
For all that you've done for
the sake of Christ our Lord,

1125
01:23:04,167 --> 01:23:05,833
let us escort you
to safety.

1126
01:23:05,917 --> 01:23:07,583
<i>My dear Maninian,</i>

1127
01:23:07,667 --> 01:23:11,583
that is exactly
where I'm going.

1128
01:23:11,625 --> 01:23:14,458
<i>What! told you
in the darkness,</i>

1129
01:23:14,500 --> 01:23:18,458
speak in the light.

1130
01:23:18,500 --> 01:23:22,667
What I whispered
in your ear,

1131
01:23:22,708 --> 01:23:27,500
proclaim from
the rooftops.

1132
01:23:29,458 --> 01:23:31,375
We must go.

1133
01:23:38,000 --> 01:23:40,875
Then take me to Jesus

1134
01:23:40,917 --> 01:23:43,792
<i>and be quick about it.</i>

1135
01:23:43,833 --> 01:23:48,083
I can't bear to be away
from him a moment longer.

1136
01:24:01,625 --> 01:24:05,042
<i>Peace, I leave you.</i>

1137
01:24:05,083 --> 01:24:08,875
<i>My peace I give you;</i>

1138
01:24:08,917 --> 01:24:10,458
<i>not as the world
gives peace,</i>

1139
01:24:10,458 --> 01:24:15,125
<i>for in this world
you will have many troubles.</i>

1140
01:24:15,167 --> 01:24:17,333
<i>But take heart,</i>

1141
01:24:17,333 --> 01:24:21,125
<i>for! have
overcome this world.</i>

1142
01:24:21,125 --> 01:24:24,583
<i>I am the way.</i>

1143
01:24:24,667 --> 01:24:27,333
<i>I am the truth.</i>

1144
01:24:27,375 --> 01:24:31,667
<i>I am the life.</i>

1145
01:24:31,750 --> 01:24:37,125
<i>No one comes to the Father,
except through me.</i>

1146
01:24:37,167 --> 01:24:40,542
<i>Everyone who asks
will receive.</i>

1147
01:24:40,625 --> 01:24:42,083
<i>He who seeks will Ô¨Ånd,</i>

1148
01:24:42,125 --> 01:24:47,167
<i>and to him who knocks
the door will be opened.</i>

1149
01:24:47,250 --> 01:24:50,458
Do not let your hearts
be troubled.

1150
01:24:50,500 --> 01:24:53,958
Do not be afraid.

1151
01:24:54,000 --> 01:24:58,500
Remain in my love.

1152
01:24:58,583 --> 01:25:04,250
Again I say,
remain in my love;

1153
01:25:05,292 --> 01:25:11,333
and surely,
I am with you always

1154
01:25:11,417 --> 01:25:15,208
to the very end
of the age.

